{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1bb2db088b","title":"是谁之过欤？","origin":"《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"172c41c51a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"1bb2db088b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"474903628a","name":"范宏贵"},{"id":"6dd61a6c39","name":"中央民族学院"},{"id":"92bee84fbb","name":"宋家丁"},{"id":"fa8141d496","name":"杨振常"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"09fa3795da","type":"title","text":"是谁之过欤？","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"34298885a5","type":"authors","text":"中央民族学院宋家丁范宏贵杨振常","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"d1634b08c7","type":"subtitle","text":"（宋家丁、范宏贵、杨振常：中央民族学院历史系民族学研究班学生,“蜜蜂社”成员）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"a25dab17fd","type":"paragraph","text":"人间憾事何其多　　妻病母悲家不和","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"ccb5a00f5f","type":"paragraph","text":"只因有了官僚味    工作分配漏洞出","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"bf2470677d","type":"paragraph","text":"查语文系1956年毕业生工作分配拖时约一年之久，于分配工作之时，学校及语文系领导主观妄测，凭印象办事，遂致颇多之人，工作分配不适，作了官僚主义的牺牲品。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"c629289b49","type":"paragraph","text":"有傅良臣者，家有双亲、爱妻慈子，居于北京西郊，本着照顾干部，填凭(平)人间天河的原则，傅良臣是应留在北京的，但院系领导不察下情，忍心傅氏抛妻弃子远居云南，傅曾呈述理由，希望照顾，但院方藉口木已成舟，拒不更改，近闻傅妻神经失常，夫妻终日吵架，父母亦悲痛欲绝，请问领导，人皆有不忍之心，汝何独无之耶！过而能改，善莫大焉，汝何独不知也耶？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"16eb84553c","type":"paragraph","text":"又查，去年语文系毕业生分配，党员悉留于北京，留于地方者，率皆政治不开展，业务学习不好之辈，似此宗派——官僚——主观——之工作方法，吾人甚恶焉！要求领导迅速改正。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"9d9285aed1","type":"paragraph","text":"傅——事要合理解决！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"a90de0d2bf","type":"paragraph","text":"使用干部要才德并重！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"},{"id":"b11ebf4db4","type":"paragraph","text":" 蜜蜂","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b"}],"page":{"id":"abc38ea415","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1bb2db088b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}